title: Tonight Show with Johnny Carson - 29th Anniversary [VHS rip]
description:
I found some old VHS tapes and decided to rip them.  I have some anniversary
episodes of the Tonight Show with Johnny Carson and Late Night with David
Letterman, as well as the 1993 MTV Music Video Awards.


This is the 29th anniversary episode of the Tonight Show with Johnny Carson.
Unfortunately, the cable was out at my house the night this aired, so the 
reception isn't great.  The sound is kinda muffled and the video quality 
isn't great, but that is to be expected given that it was taped from TV 
over 20 years ago.
